How to build and run using docker:

Build:
	$ docker build -t cryptoclass .

Run:
	$ docker run --net=host cryptoclass -d

Using net=host allows you to see the output in http://localhost:8000.

You can also set environment variables for the database:
	$ docker run --net=host -e DB_USER=db_user -e DB_PASS=db_password

You can also set DB_HOST and DB_PORT
